1
00:00:02,780 --> 00:00:05,820
[Hyeyeon: Oh, I look
completely different from yesterday?]

2
00:00:05,820 --> 00:00:07,530
[Hyeyeon: I look completely different
from yesterday.]

3
00:00:07,530 --> 00:00:10,640
[Heejin: I'm not even going
to say anything anymore.]

4
00:00:10,640 --> 00:00:14,350
[Heejin: You look exactly the same.]

5
00:00:14,350 --> 00:00:16,660
[Hyeyeon: I'll feel confident again.]

6
00:00:16,660 --> 00:00:18,760
[Heejin: Absolutely.]

7
00:00:21,470 --> 00:00:24,610
[Hyeyeon: Okay, perfect. All done.]

8
00:00:24,610 --> 00:00:28,140
[Hyeyeon: Heejin, it's already been
2 hours and 12 minutes.]

9
00:00:29,340 --> 00:00:32,930
[Heejin: Wow, really?]

10
00:00:32,930 --> 00:00:35,170
[Hyeyeon: Let's just act like we don't know.]

11
00:00:35,170 --> 00:00:37,260
[Hyeyeon: Not bad, right?]

12
00:00:37,260 --> 00:00:39,580
[Hyeyeon: That was pretty fast.]

13
00:00:39,580 --> 00:00:42,990
[Heejin: For how much prep we did,
that's actually pretty quick.]

14
00:00:42,990 --> 00:00:45,580
[Hyeyeon: Oh, true.]

15
00:00:43,750 --> 00:00:44,310
Yeah.

16
00:00:46,240 --> 00:00:48,800
[Hyeyeon: That was so quick.]
[Heejin: It is.]

17
00:00:48,820 --> 00:00:51,080
[Heejin: Do I look like I tried too hard today?]

18
00:00:51,080 --> 00:00:52,300
[Hyeyeon: You look gorgeous.]

19
00:00:52,300 --> 00:00:56,180
[Hyeyeon: I didn't think
you overdid it yesterday, either.]

20
00:00:56,180 --> 00:00:56,900
[Heejin: Really?]

21
00:00:56,900 --> 00:00:59,890
[Hyeyeon: You're always saying you tried too hard.

22
00:01:03,230 --> 00:01:05,540
[Sujin: Hello, Eunchae.]
[Eunchae: Hello.]

23
00:01:05,540 --> 00:01:08,340
[Sujin: Doing your makeup?]
[Eunchae: Yeah, what's up?]

24
00:01:08,340 --> 00:01:10,880
[Eunchae: Are you all set?]
[Sujin: Yep.]

25
00:01:10,880 --> 00:01:12,920
[Eunchae: You got up early.]
[Sujin: How do I look?]

26
00:01:12,940 --> 00:01:16,870
[Eunchae: Not bad... You look the same
as yesterday, though?]

27
00:01:18,990 --> 00:01:20,520
[Jinwoo: Oh, hey.]
[Yongkyu: Are you all set?]

28
00:01:19,850 --> 00:01:20,980
-Hey. -What?

29
00:01:20,520 --> 00:01:22,060
[Jinwoo: What?]
[Yongkyu: Are you all set?]

30
00:01:22,080 --> 00:01:22,920
[Jinwoo: Yeah.]

31
00:01:22,900 --> 00:01:24,600
[Jinwoo: Are you here to hang out?]
[Chaebe: Yeah.]

32
00:01:24,600 --> 00:01:27,050
[Jinwoo: Let's hang out.]
[Yongkyu: Everyone is still getting ready.]

33
00:01:27,660 --> 00:01:31,480
[While the guys chat to pass the time]

34
00:01:34,190 --> 00:01:37,020
[Heejin: We need to check our texts.
I'll grab your phone for you.]

35
00:01:37,020 --> 00:01:38,580
[Hyeyeon: Thanks.]

36
00:01:44,759 --> 00:01:46,280
[The Date Matching Begins]

37
00:01:46,259 --> 00:01:50,240
[Date matching begins.
Please gather in the lounge.
First come, first served]

38
00:01:50,259 --> 00:01:52,870
[Oh! First come, first served.
To the lounge!]

39
00:01:54,580 --> 00:01:55,229
[Run! Run!]
[Seungho: What does
"first come, first served" mean...]

40
00:01:55,229 --> 00:01:55,630
[Run! Run!]
[Seungho: Do we get matched based on
who gets there first?]

41
00:01:55,650 --> 00:01:58,289
[Seungho: Do we get matched based on
who gets there first?]

42
00:01:56,430 --> 00:01:58,030
-Run, run! -What's going on?

43
00:01:58,610 --> 00:02:00,870
[Chaebe takes off on his own]

44
00:01:59,530 --> 00:02:00,820
Wait up, mister!

45
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:04,680
[Seungho: Just walk.]
[Jinwoo: Wait, he just left without a word?]

46
00:02:06,980 --> 00:02:08,110
I'll be right there.

47
00:02:08,220 --> 00:02:10,919
[Sujin: Hold on, it says to gather
in the lounge for the dates.]

48
00:02:10,900 --> 00:02:14,340
[Eunchae: Ah... what's up?]
[Sujin: It's first come, first served. Wait up.]

49
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:15,490
[Sujin: Where is it?]

50
00:02:15,490 --> 00:02:17,810
[Sujin: Seriously?
They're telling us this now? This is brutal.]

51
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:24,230
[Eunchae starts to leave, then turns back]

52
00:02:24,550 --> 00:02:26,860
[Chilled out]

53
00:02:27,060 --> 00:02:30,670
[Eunchae: I figured it was already
too late to run.]

54
00:02:30,670 --> 00:02:34,160
[Eunchae: So I just gave up
and took my time.]

55
00:02:34,160 --> 00:02:37,120
[Hyeyeon: Oh, first come, first served?]

56
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:37,660
[Hyeyeon: Hurry, hurry!]

57
00:02:37,700 --> 00:02:39,820
[Hyeyeon: We made it!]

58
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:44,640
[Heejin: Hurry, hurry, hurry!]

59
00:02:46,040 --> 00:02:48,579
[Sujin: Ah, seriously, wait.]
[Hyeyeon: We won! I'm first!]

60
00:02:48,579 --> 00:02:49,460
[Heejin: I'm second!]

61
00:02:49,460 --> 00:02:50,980
[Heejin: Do we pick one?]
[Hyeyeon: Yeah! Should we draw this one?]

62
00:02:50,980 --> 00:02:52,860
[Heejin: Should we draw?]
[Sujin: I don't know.]

63
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:58,530
[8 cards on the table]

64
00:02:58,780 --> 00:03:00,920
[Hyeyeon: Do we keep them face down after picking?]
[Heejin: Should we draw?]

65
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:04,690
[Sujin: I literally sprinted down.
I was just on the second floor.]

66
00:03:04,640 --> 00:03:05,270
I'm out of breath.

67
00:03:04,690 --> 00:03:05,420
[Hyeyeon: Yeah.]

68
00:03:05,420 --> 00:03:07,780
[Hyeyeon: Even though we rushed...]

69
00:03:08,020 --> 00:03:09,430
[Hyeyeon: Even though I picked
in a bit of a rush,]

70
00:03:09,430 --> 00:03:11,870
[Hyeyeon: at least I got to pick my favorite]

71
00:03:11,870 --> 00:03:14,710
[Hyeyeon: out of the 8 cards.]

72
00:03:14,710 --> 00:03:16,590
[Hyeyeon: So getting here first
was totally worth it.]

73
00:03:17,010 --> 00:03:19,970
[Sujin: What was happening? Another date?
How were we supposed to go on the dates?]

74
00:03:19,970 --> 00:03:23,260
[Sujin: How would we know who we'd be paired
with beforehand? I wanted to know them most.]

75
00:03:25,260 --> 00:03:27,940
[Yongkyu: He ran off without even looking back.]
[Jinwoo: Exactly.]

76
00:03:27,320 --> 00:03:27,930
Chaebe!

77
00:03:27,940 --> 00:03:30,070
[Yongkyu: I'm kind of hurt.]
[Jinwoo: Chaebe!]

78
00:03:30,070 --> 00:03:33,040
[Hyeyeon: It's first come, first served. Come pick!]
[Heejin: First come, first served.]

79
00:03:33,040 --> 00:03:34,290
[Chaebe: You are so fast.]

80
00:03:34,290 --> 00:03:36,420
[Sujin: I ran my heart out.]

81
00:03:36,420 --> 00:03:37,790
[Heejin: Seriously, same here.]

82
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:39,720
-But we only had to come down the stairs. -True.

83
00:03:37,790 --> 00:03:40,050
[Hyeyeon: But we only had to run down the stairs.]

84
00:03:40,100 --> 00:03:41,560
-I was over by those stairs. -I really

85
00:03:41,350 --> 00:03:43,260
[Chaebe picks this card]

86
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:43,020
want to check out the quad room.

87
00:03:43,020 --> 00:03:46,440
-I cut straight across by the waterfall. -Hey.

88
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:49,350
[The rest of the cast arrives]

89
00:03:46,440 --> 00:03:47,560
-Hello. -Did you sleep well?

90
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:48,130
Yeah, I did.

91
00:03:48,130 --> 00:03:49,030
-Hi. -Hello.

92
00:03:49,030 --> 00:03:49,700
Hi.

93
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,980
[Jinwoo: Oh, I'm not last?]

94
00:03:50,980 --> 00:03:55,620
[Hyeyeon: It's first come, first served.
Pick a card.]

95
00:03:55,100 --> 00:03:55,620
This is the one.

96
00:03:55,620 --> 00:03:58,329
[Yongkyu: Chaebe just ran without looking back.]

97
00:03:57,160 --> 00:03:59,740
-He disappeared so fast. -We were together.

98
00:03:58,329 --> 00:03:59,560
[Yongkyu: We were all together right then.]

99
00:03:59,740 --> 00:04:01,180
-Yeah. -And he didn't even look back.

100
00:03:59,880 --> 00:04:02,500
[Awkward]

101
00:04:01,180 --> 00:04:01,980
The second he heard "first come, first served,"

102
00:04:01,980 --> 00:04:02,790
he just took off.

103
00:04:02,790 --> 00:04:04,540
[Sujin: Chaebe, you were in a massive rush.]

104
00:04:02,790 --> 00:04:04,210
-Chaebe, you were in a massive rush. -For real.

105
00:04:05,350 --> 00:04:08,520
[Yongkyu: Everyone was already seated
by the time I got here, so...]

106
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:11,580
[Yongkyu: I was basically the last one.]

107
00:04:11,580 --> 00:04:12,930
[Yongkyu: There were not many options left.]

108
00:04:14,700 --> 00:04:16,399
[Jinwoo: One card really caught my eye.]

109
00:04:16,399 --> 00:04:20,440
[Jinwoo: So I grabbed it right away.]

110
00:04:20,440 --> 00:04:23,010
[Eunchae arrives last]

111
00:04:20,980 --> 00:04:22,420
-Hey. -Morning.

112
00:04:23,010 --> 00:04:25,070
[Sujin: Eunchae, did you see me sprint out?]

113
00:04:25,070 --> 00:04:27,360
[Eunchae: You literally shot out like an arrow.]

114
00:04:27,870 --> 00:04:29,620
I was basically the Flash.

115
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:32,060
[Eunchae gets the last card]

116
00:04:32,060 --> 00:04:33,730
[Eunchae: Since all the cards were face down,]

117
00:04:33,730 --> 00:04:37,090
[Eunchae: I thought people
with matching patterns would pair up]

118
00:04:37,090 --> 00:04:39,200
[Eunchae: and go on a date.]

119
00:04:40,290 --> 00:04:42,730
[Seungho: I couldn't really figure out]

120
00:04:42,730 --> 00:04:44,560
[Seungho: what the cards meant, to be honest.]

121
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:49,150
[Seungho: Since it was first come, first served,
maybe there was a special card]

122
00:04:49,150 --> 00:04:52,190
[Seungho: that only 1 or 2 people]

123
00:04:52,190 --> 00:04:53,900
[Seungho: would end up drawing.]

124
00:04:57,240 --> 00:05:06,530
[Cast members who drew an arrow card
can ask someone out, but it must
be someone of the opposite sex.]

125
00:05:08,190 --> 00:05:09,740
[Sounds fun.]

126
00:05:09,740 --> 00:05:11,770
[Seungho: So we couldn't ask out
someone of the same sex.]

127
00:05:11,770 --> 00:05:14,900
[Seungho: It was something different,
which actually made it more interesting.]

128
00:05:14,900 --> 00:05:17,180
[Seungho: I went on a date with a guy yesterday,]

129
00:05:17,180 --> 00:05:20,810
[Seungho: so I really wanted
to go out with a girl today.]

130
00:05:20,810 --> 00:05:23,280
[Seungho: I actually liked this setup.]

131
00:05:23,540 --> 00:05:26,140
[Eunchae: First of all,
I didn't expect any restrictions]

132
00:05:26,140 --> 00:05:30,520
[Eunchae: on who we could choose.
It caught me off guard.]

133
00:05:30,520 --> 00:05:34,480
[Eunchae: I thought down the line,]

134
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:37,650
[Eunchae: we might have days
where we can only pick the same sex.]

135
00:05:37,650 --> 00:05:39,909
[Sujin: So if you get an arrow,]

136
00:05:39,909 --> 00:05:42,000
[Sujin: you can't invite the same sex,
only the opposite sex?]

137
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,950
[Seungho: Right.]

138
00:05:43,950 --> 00:05:45,120
[Sujin: At first, I was pretty happy.]

139
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:47,850
[Sujin: I wanted to go out with Heejin.]

140
00:05:47,850 --> 00:05:49,330
[Sujin: Since we had to pick the opposite sex,]

141
00:05:49,330 --> 00:05:53,350
[Sujin: Hyeyeon and Heejin
couldn't date each other.]

142
00:05:53,350 --> 00:05:56,480
[Sujin: So, I was like, "Yes!"]

143
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:59,240
[Sujin: I'd be happy no matter]

144
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:00,670
[Sujin: who picked me.]

145
00:06:01,580 --> 00:06:03,450
[Seungho: Well, I didn't get an arrow.]

146
00:06:03,450 --> 00:06:05,260
[Heejin: Me neither.]

147
00:06:05,260 --> 00:06:07,260
[The Arrow Card Holders: Hyeyeon]

148
00:06:06,730 --> 00:06:07,430
Oh my gosh.

149
00:06:07,260 --> 00:06:11,460
[I got a heart. What does a heart mean?]
[The Arrow Card Holders: Hyeyeon & Jinwoo]

150
00:06:07,980 --> 00:06:09,140
-I got an arrow. -What does a heart mean?

151
00:06:09,140 --> 00:06:11,200
-What does a heart mean? -I got a heart

152
00:06:11,460 --> 00:06:12,780
[Hyeyeon: You have to hit the heart
right in the middle.]

153
00:06:12,780 --> 00:06:14,220
[Yongkyu: Right in the middle.]

154
00:06:14,460 --> 00:06:16,150
[Seungho: So there are only hearts and arrows.]

155
00:06:16,150 --> 00:06:18,130
[Hyeyeon: Oh? You and me?]
[Jinwoo: Oh? Just the two of us?]

156
00:06:17,760 --> 00:06:19,030
-Oh wow. -This is it.

157
00:06:18,420 --> 00:06:21,700
[Hyeyeon and Jinwoo
earn the right to choose their dates]

158
00:06:19,030 --> 00:06:22,500
-They get to pick. -One girl and one guy.

159
00:06:23,630 --> 00:06:25,690
[Upset]

160
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:29,320
[Heejin: Ah, I really thought
things would go my way.]

161
00:06:29,320 --> 00:06:31,730
[Heejin: Seriously, what was the point
of rushing down early?]

162
00:06:31,730 --> 00:06:35,000
[Heejin: That was kind of a bummer, honestly.]

163
00:06:35,290 --> 00:06:37,850
[Upset]

164
00:06:38,320 --> 00:06:40,290
[Yongkyu: When I realized
I was the one being chosen,]

165
00:06:40,290 --> 00:06:41,500
[Yongkyu: it actually felt like a relief.]

166
00:06:41,500 --> 00:06:44,409
[Yongkyu: Instead of me
having to choose someone to date,]

167
00:06:44,409 --> 00:06:46,970
[Yongkyu: it actually feels easier]

168
00:06:46,970 --> 00:06:48,170
[Yongkyu: to just be the one being chosen.]

169
00:06:48,170 --> 00:06:49,230
[Sujin: Man, I'm so jealous of you.]

170
00:06:49,230 --> 00:06:51,400
[Sujin: Jinwoo, you either get the secret room]

171
00:06:51,400 --> 00:06:53,370
[Sujin: or you play Cupid and shoot the arrow.]

172
00:06:53,370 --> 00:06:55,710
[Jinwoo: Ugh, why does this always happen to me?]
[Sujin: You've got your hands full.]

173
00:06:55,710 --> 00:06:56,590
[Jinwoo: You flatter me.]

174
00:06:56,590 --> 00:06:59,640
[Seungho: Who are you going with?]

175
00:06:59,640 --> 00:07:01,870
[Jinwoo: I have no idea.]

176
00:07:01,870 --> 00:07:03,000
[Yongkyu: Think it over carefully.]

177
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:05,820
[Hyeyeon: Seriously.]

178
00:07:06,450 --> 00:07:08,460
[Beaming]

179
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:13,450
[Hyeyeon: I wanted to choose
between Seungho and Sujin.]

180
00:07:13,450 --> 00:07:16,250
[Hyeyeon: Because]

181
00:07:16,250 --> 00:07:19,500
[Hyeyeon: I like them both about the same.]

182
00:07:19,500 --> 00:07:22,620
[Hyeyeon: Seungho went
to the secret room yesterday.]

183
00:07:22,620 --> 00:07:25,150
[Hyeyeon: He's already much closer
to Jinwoo than to me.]

184
00:07:25,150 --> 00:07:29,260
[Hyeyeon: They might have already figured out
where they stand with each other.]

185
00:07:29,210 --> 00:07:30,750
I was worried that if I picked him,

186
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:33,430
["What if he's not into me?"]

187
00:07:33,810 --> 00:07:37,040
[Seungho: The opposite-sex rule
is actually pretty fun.]

188
00:07:34,700 --> 00:07:35,630
Yes.

189
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:39,190
[Seungho: Since I already dated Jinwoo yesterday,]

190
00:07:39,190 --> 00:07:42,190
[Seungho: it'd be nice to go on a date]

191
00:07:42,190 --> 00:07:44,120
[Seungho: with Hyeyeon today.]

192
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:46,640
[Hyeyeon: So, Jinwoo, have you decided?]

193
00:07:46,640 --> 00:07:50,340
[Jinwoo: Oh, uh... pretty much.]

194
00:07:51,670 --> 00:07:53,550
[Yongkyu: Come on, you've got to lock it in.]

195
00:07:53,550 --> 00:07:54,920
[Yongkyu: You can't just wing it.]
[Jinwoo: I'm working on it.]

196
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:57,250
[Heejin: Have you decided?]
[Hyeyeon: No, not yet.]

197
00:07:57,250 --> 00:07:58,580
[Jinwoo: Yeah, it's a tough choice.]

198
00:07:59,770 --> 00:08:01,220
[Seungho: It's hard.]
[Hyeyeon: I'm so torn.]

199
00:08:01,490 --> 00:08:03,150
[Torn]

200
00:08:05,290 --> 00:08:08,170
[Hyeyeon: I can't decide.]

201
00:08:08,170 --> 00:08:11,540
[Heejin: Why are you acting like this?]

202
00:08:11,540 --> 00:08:13,630
[Sujin: That is so T.]

203
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:16,410
[Hyeyeon: Oh my.]

204
00:08:17,970 --> 00:08:19,950
[Hyeyeon: Ah, this is so hard.]

205
00:08:19,950 --> 00:08:21,650
[Yongkyu: You don't have to go first.]

206
00:08:21,650 --> 00:08:23,570
[Hyeyeon: Okay, I'll let you go first, Jinwoo.]

207
00:08:23,570 --> 00:08:27,660
[Yongkyu: One of you has to pick eventually,
you both got the card.]
[Sujin: That's not what's on Jinwoo's mind.]

208
00:08:28,490 --> 00:08:32,520
[Jinwoo: Here we go again...]
[Hyeyeon: I'm waiting for you.]

209
00:08:34,100 --> 00:08:39,720
[Who will Jinwoo choose?]

210
00:08:41,549 --> 00:08:44,370
[Jinwoo: Today, Eunchae...]

211
00:08:44,410 --> 00:08:46,390
So today, Eunchae...

212
00:08:47,650 --> 00:08:49,480
[Flustered]

213
00:08:47,910 --> 00:08:49,110
and I will go on a date.

214
00:08:52,680 --> 00:08:55,750
[Jinwoo: Honestly, Hyeyeon
was the first person I thought of.]

215
00:08:55,750 --> 00:08:57,440
[Jinwoo: But when I looked at her,]

216
00:08:57,440 --> 00:09:00,040
[Jinwoo: she had the exact same arrow card
as I did.]

217
00:09:00,040 --> 00:09:02,130
[Jinwoo: So that was a bummer.]

218
00:09:02,130 --> 00:09:05,170
[Jinwoo: But Eunchae made a really strong]

219
00:09:05,170 --> 00:09:06,810
[Jinwoo: first impression on me.]

220
00:09:06,810 --> 00:09:09,000
[Jinwoo: So I felt like I]

221
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:11,790
[Jinwoo: had to ask her]

222
00:09:11,790 --> 00:09:12,740
[Jinwoo: out on a date.]

223
00:09:14,170 --> 00:09:17,640
[Eunchae: I wondered why he picked me.]

224
00:09:17,640 --> 00:09:19,690
[Eunchae: I was a bit nervous, but]

225
00:09:19,690 --> 00:09:23,300
[Eunchae: it always feels good to get chosen.]

226
00:09:24,560 --> 00:09:26,660
[Seungho: It bothered me a little.]

227
00:09:26,660 --> 00:09:28,810
[Seungho: It was a date
with the opposite sex.]

228
00:09:28,810 --> 00:09:32,180
[Seungho: But did he like Eunchae best]

229
00:09:32,180 --> 00:09:33,510
[Seungho: out of all the girls?]

230
00:09:33,510 --> 00:09:35,430
[Seungho: If he could choose from anyone at all,]

231
00:09:35,430 --> 00:09:39,560
[Seungho: I thought he'd choose me.]

232
00:09:40,870 --> 00:09:42,740
[Sighs]

233
00:09:43,050 --> 00:09:44,850
[Hyeyeon: Today, I'm...]

234
00:09:51,670 --> 00:09:53,360
[Hyeyeon: picking Seungho.]

235
00:09:53,400 --> 00:09:54,840
I pick Seungho.

236
00:09:54,400 --> 00:09:56,640
[Surprised]

237
00:10:00,520 --> 00:10:03,180
[Hyeyeon: Since I could only pick a guy,]

238
00:10:03,180 --> 00:10:04,970
[Hyeyeon: between Seungho and Sujin,]

239
00:10:04,970 --> 00:10:06,700
[Hyeyeon: Sujin was naturally ruled out.]

240
00:10:06,700 --> 00:10:09,800
[Hyeyeon: So I went with Seungho.]

241
00:10:09,800 --> 00:10:13,500
