244
00:10:18,830 --> 00:10:22,580
[Seungho: I kept hoping she'd pick me.]

245
00:10:22,580 --> 00:10:24,850
[Seungho: The second she called my name...]

246
00:10:25,150 --> 00:10:31,160
["I was so glad it was me."]

247
00:10:28,270 --> 00:10:29,040
It was me.

248
00:10:29,260 --> 00:10:30,880
That's what I thought.

249
00:10:33,520 --> 00:10:34,970
[Jinwoo: I never saw that coming.]

250
00:10:34,970 --> 00:10:36,910
[Jinwoo: What was this?]

251
00:10:36,910 --> 00:10:39,730
[Jinwoo: What was even happening?]

252
00:10:41,740 --> 00:10:44,450
["I think I was a little jealous."]

253
00:10:45,510 --> 00:10:47,800
[Heejin: When she picked Seungho,
I thought, "Oh? This is interesting."]

254
00:10:47,800 --> 00:10:50,840
[Heejin: This was getting interesting.]

255
00:10:52,250 --> 00:10:54,510
[Yongkyu: Getting chosen was great, of course.]

256
00:10:54,510 --> 00:10:58,190
