even if I got picked, I might mess it up.]

257
00:10:58,190 --> 00:10:59,770
[Yongkyu: I'd rather let things happen naturally]

258
00:10:59,770 --> 00:11:01,760
[Yongkyu: and get to know each other
through daily life.]

259
00:11:01,760 --> 00:11:05,860
[Yongkyu: I wanted to go on a date
when the spark is actually there.]

260
00:11:05,860 --> 00:11:08,350
[Yongkyu: If she had picked me,
I would have felt]

261
00:11:08,350 --> 00:11:11,750
[Yongkyu: way too pressured.]

262
00:11:12,500 --> 00:11:15,360
[Chaebe: It was a bummer.
It was already day two,]

263
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:18,120
[Chaebe: and I really wanted to go on a date.]

264
00:11:18,120 --> 00:11:21,010
[Chaebe: I just felt so, so disappointed.]

265
00:11:21,690 --> 00:11:25,070
[Heejin looks upset]

266
00:11:26,490 --> 00:11:29,240
[Sujin: Well, at least I got]

267
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:33,550
