268
00:11:33,550 --> 00:11:34,810
[Sujin: Congrats, congrats.]

269
00:11:34,810 --> 00:11:37,210
[Jinwoo: Congrats, congrats.]

270
00:11:38,950 --> 00:11:40,750
[Hyeyeon: Should we go get ready for our date?]

271
00:11:40,750 --> 00:11:41,790
[Seungho: Sure.]

272
00:11:45,400 --> 00:11:47,110
[Hyeyeon: What are you wearing?]

273
00:11:47,110 --> 00:11:49,190
[Seungho: I was thinking of wearing]

274
00:11:49,190 --> 00:11:52,120
[Seungho: a bomber jacket and...]
[Hyeyeon: Oh, that'll look great on you.]

275
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:56,050
[Seungho: I'll wear this underneath with jeans.]
[Hyeyeon: Oh, very cool.]

276
00:11:56,150 --> 00:11:58,280
-What should I wear then? -Anything works.

277
00:11:58,280 --> 00:11:59,060
I was going to... -I can

278
00:11:59,060 --> 00:11:59,850
change into something else.

279
00:11:59,830 --> 00:12:02,140
[Hyeyeon: Then maybe]

280
00:12:02,140 --> 00:12:04,960
[Hyeyeon: I'll wear jeans too.]

281
00:12:04,380 --> 00:12:04,970
Sounds good.

282
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:06,710
[Hyeyeon: That should work, right?]
[Seungho: Yeah, sounds perfect.]

283
00:12:06,710 --> 00:12:12,160
[Seungho: I don't know much
about girls' fashion anyway.]

284
00:12:12,380 --> 00:12:15,170
[Heejin: The guy I'm most interested in]

285
00:12:15,170 --> 00:12:18,000
[Heejin: and the guy
I'm second most curious about]

286
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:21,120
