288
00:12:23,980 --> 00:12:25,690
[Heejin: The more I thought about it,
the more confused I got.]

289
00:12:27,390 --> 00:12:29,600
[Hyeyeon: How am I doing?]

290
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:33,560
[Seungho: Pretty good. What do you mean?]
[Hyeyeon: As an ESTP.]

291
00:12:34,130 --> 00:12:37,050
[Hmm...]

292
00:12:37,050 --> 00:12:40,860
[Seungho: It's not weird at all.]

293
00:12:40,860 --> 00:12:43,690
[Seungho: You look great. Very pretty.]
[Hyeyeon: Ah, thanks.]

294
00:12:43,690 --> 00:12:47,120
[Hyeyeon: I was a little nervous because he'd]

295
00:12:47,120 --> 00:12:49,590
[Hyeyeon: probably be wondering why I picked him.]

296
00:12:49,590 --> 00:12:52,480
[Hyeyeon: It'd be good to talk about it.]

297
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:55,140
[Hyeyeon: But anyway, But since I was]

298
00:12:55,140 --> 00:12:58,170
[Hyeyeon: the one who chose him,]

299
00:12:58,170 --> 00:13:00,500
[Hyeyeon: I was really nervous.]

300
00:13:00,920 --> 00:13:02,940
[Jinwoo: How do I look today?]

301
00:13:05,130 --> 00:13:07,420
[Spins around]

302
00:13:07,620 --> 00:13:11,080
[Seungho: Like an elementary schooler.
It's cute and stylish.]

303
00:13:11,080 --> 00:13:12,460
[Jinwoo: Ah, like a school kid?]

304
00:13:12,460 --> 00:13:15,200
[Seungho: A little bit? But it actually works...]
[Jinwoo: A little bit?]

305
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:17,330
[Jinwoo: Should I make this my signature look?]

306
00:13:17,330 --> 00:13:21,070
[Seungho: No, it's just the vibe of the clothes.]
[Jinwoo: Ah, really?]

307
00:13:21,070 --> 00:13:23,660
[Jinwoo: Do I look like a school kid?]
[Heejin: Huh? Oh...]

308
00:13:23,660 --> 00:13:27,000
[Heejin: But that's the whole point, right?]

309
00:13:25,210 --> 00:13:25,780
Is it?

310
00:13:27,860 --> 00:13:30,840
[Eunchae, Jinwoo's Date]

311
00:13:35,020 --> 00:13:40,170
[Eunchae: Jinwoo was full of energy yesterday.]

312
00:13:40,170 --> 00:13:44,080
[Eunchae: Going on a date with him would be fun.]

313
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:49,470
[Eunchae: He seemed great at breaking the ice,
so I was excited.]

314
00:13:49,470 --> 00:13:51,690
[Hyeyeon: We're heading out!]
[Jinwoo: We're leaving!]

315
00:13:51,690 --> 00:13:54,330
[Heejin: Have fun! Get going!]
[Jinwoo: See you later.]

316
00:13:54,830 --> 00:13:58,600
[What kind of heart-fluttering moments
await them on their first official date?]

317
00:14:21,560 --> 00:14:22,620
We're at the beach!

318
00:14:24,150 --> 00:14:26,590
[Seungho: Whoa, my feet are sinking
right into the sand.]

319
00:14:26,780 --> 00:14:27,670
[This is nice.]

320
00:14:28,380 --> 00:14:29,670
[Seungho: Wait, this is the first date for us.]

321
00:14:29,670 --> 00:14:30,960
[Seungho: Our very first date, right?]

322
00:14:30,960 --> 00:14:33,310
[Hyeyeon: Oh, right!]

323
00:14:34,310 --> 00:14:36,210
[Seungho: We went surfing.]

324
00:14:36,210 --> 00:14:38,830
[Seungho: Honestly, I never expected this.]

325
00:14:38,830 --> 00:14:42,690
[Seungho: I was pretty worried
and overthinking it.]

326
00:14:44,960 --> 00:14:48,960
[Hyeyeon: Making a shared memory like surfing]

327
00:14:48,960 --> 00:14:51,150
[Hyeyeon: felt like a really good idea.]

328
00:14:52,810 --> 00:14:57,110
[Hyeyeon and Seungho arrive for surfing lessons]

329
00:14:53,690 --> 00:14:54,720
Hello.

330
00:14:55,210 --> 00:14:56,870
-Hello. -Hello.

331
00:14:57,870 --> 00:15:00,110
[Both of you, get on your boards.]

332
00:15:00,110 --> 00:15:03,400
[I'll quickly show you the "pop-up"—
how to stand up on the board.]

333
00:15:03,610 --> 00:15:04,390
Get down.

334
00:15:04,070 --> 00:15:07,700
[Touching a surfboard for the first time]

335
00:15:08,060 --> 00:15:09,630
[That's wild.]

336
00:15:10,400 --> 00:15:12,560
[Just follow my cues.]

337
00:15:12,560 --> 00:15:14,410
[Let's try paddling. Paddle!]

338
00:15:14,410 --> 00:15:17,180
[Lift your chest and start paddling.]

339
00:15:17,740 --> 00:15:21,990
[Focused]

340
00:15:18,050 --> 00:15:20,890
Great, reach forward.

341
00:15:20,890 --> 00:15:22,120
Just like swimming.

342
00:15:22,190 --> 00:15:23,770
[Next is the push.]

343
00:15:23,790 --> 00:15:26,020
When I say push, place your hands... good.

344
00:15:25,420 --> 00:15:26,300
[In one swift motion]

345
00:15:26,580 --> 00:15:28,980
[Keep your elbows straight. Perfect.]

346
00:15:30,020 --> 00:15:33,430
[When I count "one,"
bring your right heel and knee together.]

347
00:15:33,430 --> 00:15:36,010
[Bring it right here.]

348
00:15:36,670 --> 00:15:37,400
OK, perfect.

349
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:40,350
Right here, and then...

350
00:15:40,730 --> 00:15:42,710
[When I count "two,"
bring your back foot forward.]

351
00:15:42,330 --> 00:15:43,030
Two!

352
00:15:44,430 --> 00:15:45,290
[Sliding]

353
00:15:45,290 --> 00:15:46,210
[Like this?]

354
00:15:46,210 --> 00:15:47,480
[Not bad, not bad.]

355
00:15:47,480 --> 00:15:49,860
[Keep your eyes looking straight ahead. Exactly.]

356
00:15:49,860 --> 00:15:51,350
[Hold that pose, use the power
in your front foot,]

357
00:15:51,350 --> 00:15:53,500
[and just stand straight up.]

358
00:15:54,810 --> 00:15:56,200
Good, stand up.

359
00:15:56,200 --> 00:15:58,290
Keep balance.

360
00:15:57,030 --> 00:15:58,280
[Stumbles]

361
00:15:58,930 --> 00:15:59,970
OK, great.

362
00:15:59,550 --> 00:16:00,620
[Wobbles]

363
00:15:59,970 --> 00:16:02,480
Just do the exact same thing in the water. Got it?

364
00:16:02,480 --> 00:16:03,410
-Got it. -Got it.

365
00:16:04,160 --> 00:16:06,000
[Hyeyeon: Did you get it?]
[Seungho: I'm still a bit lost.]

366
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:07,430
[Seungho: But it should be super fun.]

367
00:16:07,340 --> 00:16:07,800
Really?

368
00:16:07,430 --> 00:16:09,350
[Seungho: I'll probably wipe out a lot, though.]

369
00:16:08,750 --> 00:16:09,350
Yeah, definitely.

370
00:16:09,350 --> 00:16:11,680
[Hyeyeon: I was shaking just trying to stand up.]

371
00:16:11,680 --> 00:16:15,120
[Seungho: I didn't really get that first foot movement.]

372
00:16:18,030 --> 00:16:19,290
[Hyeyeon: Try it again.]

373
00:16:19,290 --> 00:16:20,730
[Seungho: Should I?]

374
00:16:20,730 --> 00:16:21,710
[Seungho: By myself?]

375
00:16:21,710 --> 00:16:23,140
[Hyeyeon: I'll watch.]

376
00:16:22,280 --> 00:16:22,920
Yes.

377
00:16:24,380 --> 00:16:26,320
Paddle.

378
00:16:26,660 --> 00:16:27,740
Stand up.

379
00:16:27,740 --> 00:16:28,670
Foot.

380
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:30,880
Then step forward.

381
00:16:31,750 --> 00:16:32,860
And stand up.

382
00:16:32,860 --> 00:16:33,930
OK, great.

383
00:16:34,350 --> 00:16:37,740
[Let's change quickly and hit the waves.]

384
00:16:40,240 --> 00:16:43,240
[The cool sea awaits Hyeyeon and Seungho]

385
00:16:41,990 --> 00:16:43,030
-This way. -Okay.

386
00:16:44,240 --> 00:16:46,000
[Think we can do this? Let's do this!]

387
00:16:46,000 --> 00:16:46,960
[Honestly, I have no idea.]

388
00:16:48,240 --> 00:16:49,890
[Nervous]

389
00:16:51,960 --> 00:16:53,160
[Hyeyeon: Can you stand up on the board?]

390
00:16:53,160 --> 00:16:54,710
[Seungho: No clue.]

391
00:16:54,710 --> 00:16:56,680
[Hyeyeon: Wait, it's freezing!]

392
00:17:00,880 --> 00:17:01,610
[Seungho: Whoa, it really is cold!]

393
00:17:01,610 --> 00:17:02,980
[Hyeyeon: Hold on!]

394
00:17:03,830 --> 00:17:04,660
Wait a second.

395
00:17:04,589 --> 00:17:06,130
[Stamping feet]

396
00:17:06,780 --> 00:17:08,069
[Hyeyeon: My feet are freezing!]

397
00:17:08,069 --> 00:17:10,280
[You're good, you're good.
You'll get used to it fast.]

398
00:17:15,630 --> 00:17:18,540
[Keep the board vertical. Don't push it.]

399
00:17:18,540 --> 00:17:19,560
[Panicking]
[Seungho: How are we supposed
to balance like this?]

400
00:17:21,730 --> 00:17:24,500
[You just have to push through.]

401
00:17:22,560 --> 00:17:23,369
Hold on tight.

402
00:17:25,210 --> 00:17:25,770
OK.

403
00:17:25,280 --> 00:17:27,900
[Now lie down on the board.]

404
00:17:27,900 --> 00:17:29,310
[Alright, lie down on the board.]

405
00:17:29,310 --> 00:17:30,930
[The guy keeps holding onto the board!]

406
00:17:33,010 --> 00:17:33,860
Again, again.

407
00:17:34,440 --> 00:17:35,260
Get ready.

408
00:17:35,260 --> 00:17:36,500
Ready to surf.

409
00:17:36,780 --> 00:17:37,630
Here we go.

410
00:17:37,860 --> 00:17:39,730
[You okay?] [No!]

411
00:17:39,790 --> 00:17:40,660
Push off.

412
00:17:43,250 --> 00:17:46,340
[First attempt failed]

413
00:17:47,440 --> 00:17:49,050
[Come on up, sir.]

414
00:17:49,390 --> 00:17:50,010
Okay.

415
00:17:51,350 --> 00:17:52,300
Get down!

416
00:17:53,760 --> 00:17:55,070
Push, push.

417
00:17:57,300 --> 00:17:59,250
Stand up, stand up, stand up!

418
00:17:57,450 --> 00:17:58,450
[Excited]

419
00:18:01,290 --> 00:18:02,860
[Sliding]

420
00:18:08,330 --> 00:18:10,810
[Seungho: Oh man, my face is completely soaked.]

421
00:18:12,600 --> 00:18:13,570
[Hyeyeon: Hold on with your hands.]

422
00:18:12,680 --> 00:18:17,010
[Hyeyeon's turn again]

423
00:18:15,450 --> 00:18:16,050
Ready.

424
00:18:17,720 --> 00:18:18,600
Push.

425
00:18:19,140 --> 00:18:20,010
Stand up.

426
00:18:25,310 --> 00:18:28,870
[Hyeyeon successfully pops up]

427
00:18:28,670 --> 00:18:29,590
Great job!

428
00:18:31,340 --> 00:18:32,870
[Seungho: Whoa, how did you do that?]

429
00:18:32,870 --> 00:18:33,970
[Seungho: How did you manage that?]

430
00:18:33,970 --> 00:18:34,790
[Seungho: You did it?]

431
00:18:35,110 --> 00:18:36,780
[Hyeyeon: I did it!]

432
00:18:37,810 --> 00:18:40,240
[Excited]

433
00:18:42,520 --> 00:18:46,610
[Seungho's turn again]

434
00:18:48,320 --> 00:18:50,030
[Fighting!]

435
00:18:57,870 --> 00:19:02,850
[Seungho manages to pop-up too]

436
00:19:07,840 --> 00:19:09,130
[He's up!]

437
00:19:10,320 --> 00:19:11,580
[Clapping]

438
00:19:11,910 --> 00:19:13,200
[This is so fun!]

439
00:19:20,570 --> 00:19:26,180
[Hyeyeon and Seungho take a breather
after a successful surf]

440
00:19:20,710 --> 00:19:21,750
That wasn't easy.

441
00:19:22,800 --> 00:19:23,540
Seriously.

442
00:19:26,440 --> 00:19:27,920
[Seungho: Do I look like a total mess?]

443
00:19:27,920 --> 00:19:30,250
[Seungho: My hair is all over the place.]
[Hyeyeon: Just push it back.]

444
00:19:30,250 --> 00:19:31,910
[Hyeyeon: Come here.]

445
00:19:34,630 --> 00:19:37,340
[Seungho: Can you do it for me? I can't see.]

446
00:19:37,340 --> 00:19:38,580
[Hyeyeon: Like this?]

447
00:19:39,340 --> 00:19:40,080
A little bit.

448
00:19:40,080 --> 00:19:41,090
Don't slick it all back.

449
00:19:41,090 --> 00:19:42,250
Not the whole thing.

450
00:19:43,650 --> 00:19:44,770
There.

451
00:19:48,250 --> 00:19:53,040
[They grow closer after surfing]

452
00:19:48,580 --> 00:19:49,460
How is it?

453
00:19:50,500 --> 00:19:52,460
I don't know, I can't see it.

454
00:19:53,060 --> 00:19:53,990
But...

455
00:19:55,910 --> 00:19:57,490
[Hyeyeon: Ugh, my hands won't stop shaking.]

456
00:19:57,490 --> 00:20:00,010
[Seungho: Hey, the waves were just massive today.]

457
00:20:00,010 --> 00:20:03,260
[Seungho: The instructor told me to wait,
but the water was just too strong.]

458
00:20:04,220 --> 00:20:07,540
[Seungho: These huge waves
kept crashing right into my face.]

459
00:20:07,540 --> 00:20:09,280
[Seungho: I couldn't wait.]

460
00:20:09,940 --> 00:20:10,930
-My mouth... -But you stood up, right?

461
00:20:10,510 --> 00:20:13,490
[Seungho: But you stood up, right?
Was that your second try?]

462
00:20:10,930 --> 00:20:11,930
Was that your second try?

463
00:20:11,930 --> 00:20:14,190
-I stood up once. -Didn't I stand up, too?

464
00:20:14,310 --> 00:20:15,670
[Seungho: Honestly,
I didn't even realize I was up.]

465
00:20:15,670 --> 00:20:18,520
[Hyeyeon: Same here. I stood up
for a split second and immediately wiped out.]

466
00:20:17,890 --> 00:20:18,510
-Immediately wiped out. -Right?

467
00:20:18,510 --> 00:20:19,650
But at least...

468
00:20:19,630 --> 00:20:25,000
[A precious memory for just the two of them
by the endless sea]

469
00:20:19,650 --> 00:20:21,240
We still stood up.

470
00:20:21,240 --> 00:20:23,210
-We stood up. -Not bad for a first time.

471
00:20:23,210 --> 00:20:24,420
-Did we make it? -We managed to hold on.

472
00:20:24,420 --> 00:20:25,420
Pretty good.

473
00:20:26,920 --> 00:20:30,200
[Seungho: Honestly, it was a little awkward]

474
00:20:30,200 --> 00:20:31,740
[Seungho: until we started surfing.]

475
00:20:31,740 --> 00:20:35,430
[Seungho: But Hyeyeon was so good
at keeping the conversation going.]

476
00:20:35,430 --> 00:20:38,320
[Seungho: She made me feel like
we really connected.]

477
00:20:38,320 --> 00:20:41,590
[Seungho: We were really comfortable
around each other.]

478
00:20:41,590 --> 00:20:44,020
[Seungho: We've gotten way closer.]

479
00:20:44,480 --> 00:20:47,120
[Hyeyeon: We changed clothes after surfing,]

480
00:20:47,120 --> 00:20:51,190
[Hyeyeon: and just splashed around
in the water together.]

481
00:20:51,190 --> 00:20:56,010
[Hyeyeon: It was my first time hanging
out in the water with a guy.]

482
00:20:56,010 --> 00:20:58,920
[Hyeyeon: it felt really new and exciting.]

483
00:20:59,880 --> 00:21:03,280
["So happy"]

484
00:21:04,480 --> 00:21:05,830
[Hyeyeon: Should we draw a heart?]

485
00:21:05,830 --> 00:21:07,020
[Seungho: Sure.]

486
00:21:08,120 --> 00:21:09,020
How come?

487
00:21:08,920 --> 00:21:12,510
[A special memory for the two of them]

488
00:21:10,740 --> 00:21:11,470
Start over.

489
00:21:12,920 --> 00:21:16,660
[Hyeyeon: He wanted to build a sandcastle,
and while we were at it,]

490
00:21:16,660 --> 00:21:20,590
[Hyeyeon: I suggested drawing a heart, so we did.]

491
00:21:20,590 --> 00:21:26,290
[Hyeyeon: But then Seungho went,
"Mine looks better."]

492
00:21:26,290 --> 00:21:28,070
[Hyeyeon: That little moment
let me see his real personality.]

493
00:21:29,040 --> 00:21:31,240
I thought it was really romantic.

494
00:21:29,800 --> 00:21:32,900
["So romantic"]

495
00:21:34,850 --> 00:21:39,900
[They share a special moment]

496
00:21:40,820 --> 00:21:43,250
[Hyeyeon: Did you have fun?]
[Seungho: Yeah, today was great.]

497
00:21:43,250 --> 00:21:45,810
[Hyeyeon: Me too. Even though
I'm a little exhausted.]

498
00:21:45,810 --> 00:21:47,230
[Seungho: Yeah, it was definitely tiring.]

499
00:21:47,230 --> 00:21:49,370
[Seungho: But it was worth it.]
[Hyeyeon: Yeah, it was super fun.]

500
00:21:49,840 --> 00:21:52,290
[Hyeyeon: Ah, I had the best time.]

501
00:21:52,290 --> 00:21:54,580
[Hyeyeon, let's grab a drink.]
[Alright.]

502
00:21:56,470 --> 00:22:00,190
[Enjoying a sweet break after surfing]

503
00:22:00,560 --> 00:22:01,780
[Seungho: what do you usually drink?]

504
00:22:01,780 --> 00:22:04,530
[Hyeyeon: I don't usually drink coffee.]

505
00:22:04,530 --> 00:22:05,470
[Hyeyeon Soda?]

506
00:22:05,470 --> 00:22:08,000
[Seungho: Oh, same here.]
[Hyeyeon: Oh, really? Then...]

507
00:22:09,120 --> 00:22:12,230
[Seungho: I'll go with grapefruit.]
[Grapefruit?]

508
00:22:12,230 --> 00:22:14,340
[Hyeyeon: I'll get grapefruit, too.]

509
00:22:14,340 --> 00:22:15,810
[Hyeyeon, what do you want to eat?]

510
00:22:16,150 --> 00:22:17,610
[Seungho: Maybe a croissant?]

511
00:22:17,480 --> 00:22:18,190
A croissant?

512
00:22:17,610 --> 00:22:20,950
[Hyeyeon: Let's start with one croissant then?]
[Seungho: Sounds good.]

513
00:22:20,950 --> 00:22:25,820
[Hyeyeon: 2 grapefruit sodas
and a croissant, please.]

514
00:22:25,280 --> 00:22:26,790
Grapefruit soda and a croissant.

515
00:22:26,300 --> 00:22:27,730
[Glancing over]

516
00:22:28,020 --> 00:22:28,880
[Quietly]

517
00:22:28,880 --> 00:22:31,890
[Hyeyeon: The bracelets...]

518
00:22:31,890 --> 00:22:35,330
[Seungho: Want to pick a pair?]
[Hyeyeon: As a souvenir for today?]

519
00:22:33,880 --> 00:22:34,520
Sure.

520
00:22:35,330 --> 00:22:37,520
[Seungho: What color do you like?]
[Hyeyeon: Should we pick for each other?]

521
00:22:37,110 --> 00:22:38,660
-Sure. -What color do you like?

522
00:22:37,520 --> 00:22:39,740
[Hyeyeon: What color do you like?]

523
00:22:39,730 --> 00:22:40,500
Or...

524
00:22:40,160 --> 00:22:43,230
[Hyeyeon: Let's choose one for each other.]

525
00:22:43,230 --> 00:22:45,570
[Seungho: Why don't you pick one for me?]

526
00:22:44,030 --> 00:22:44,680
Okay.

527
00:22:45,870 --> 00:22:47,400
I picked one that's kind of hit-or-miss.

528
00:22:45,880 --> 00:22:48,800
[What bracelet did Hyeyeon pick for Seungho?]

529
00:22:49,180 --> 00:22:50,760
[Carefully]

530
00:22:51,510 --> 00:22:52,840
[Hyeyeon: This actually looks pretty good on you.]

531
00:22:52,840 --> 00:22:55,040
[Hyeyeon: Ah, you don't like it?]
[Seungho: No, I do.]

532
00:22:55,760 --> 00:22:57,530
[Seungho: I think I prefer this one.]

533
00:22:57,530 --> 00:22:58,700
[Hyeyeon: How about this one then?]

534
00:22:57,640 --> 00:22:58,970
How about this one then?

535
00:22:58,980 --> 00:23:00,150
-This one. -I knew it.

536
00:22:59,720 --> 00:23:02,900
[Seungho goes with his first choice]

537
00:23:01,240 --> 00:23:02,970
I'll pick this one for Seungho.

538
00:23:03,270 --> 00:23:05,660
[Hyeyeon: Now you pick one for me.]

539
00:23:06,120 --> 00:23:08,480
[Seungho: I immediately thought of pink.]
[Hyeyeon: Agreed.]

540
00:23:08,540 --> 00:23:10,190
-Let's put them on. -Okay.

541
00:23:10,650 --> 00:23:13,740
[They buy matching bracelets
to remember their first date]

542
00:23:11,190 --> 00:23:12,790
-Let me check you out. -Okay.

543
00:23:16,660 --> 00:23:17,820
[Oh? Let's open it up.]

544
00:23:18,030 --> 00:23:19,630
[Alright.]

545
00:23:19,810 --> 00:23:21,040
[Hyeyeon: You like this color, right?]

546
00:23:21,040 --> 00:23:23,200
[Hyeyeon: It really suits you.]

547
00:23:23,910 --> 00:23:25,520
[Fumbling]

548
00:23:26,500 --> 00:23:27,780
[Seungho: Where do I open this?]

549
00:23:27,780 --> 00:23:29,130
[Picks up]

550
00:23:33,930 --> 00:23:37,510
[Seungho: I think I got too much saltwater
in my eyes earlier.]
[Hyeyeon: Yeah, probably.]

551
00:23:37,840 --> 00:23:40,510
[Hyeyeon helps him open it]

552
00:23:40,910 --> 00:23:42,350
[Embarrassed]

553
00:23:43,260 --> 00:23:43,980
Thanks.

554
00:23:53,000 --> 00:23:54,140
I got it.

555
00:23:54,280 --> 00:23:56,570
-Did you braid this yourself? -All done.

556
00:23:57,160 --> 00:23:59,130
[Hyeyeon: Want me to put it on you?] [Seungho: Yeah, please.]

557
00:23:59,500 --> 00:24:01,700
