558
00:24:03,630 --> 00:24:04,560
It's on.

559
00:24:03,680 --> 00:24:04,940
[Glancing over]

560
00:24:05,480 --> 00:24:08,040
[Hyeyeon helps Seungho out]

561
00:24:09,310 --> 00:24:10,440
[What do you think?]

562
00:24:10,670 --> 00:24:14,250
[Seungho: I do prefer someone who takes charge.]

563
00:24:14,250 --> 00:24:19,530
[Seungho: She really looked after me,
and I liked that.]

564
00:24:19,530 --> 00:24:21,400
[Hyeyeon: I'll just put mine on myself.]

565
00:24:21,400 --> 00:24:22,990
[Hyeyeon: Just tighten it for me.]

566
00:24:23,210 --> 00:24:23,940
To here?

567
00:24:25,540 --> 00:24:26,420
[Seungho: Like this?]

568
00:24:26,420 --> 00:24:28,510
[Seungho: Yeah, this short string.]

569
00:24:29,430 --> 00:24:31,010
[Trying hard]

570
00:24:30,080 --> 00:24:31,600
Pull both sides.

571
00:24:37,250 --> 00:24:39,270
[Seungho: Do you wear bracelets often?]

572
00:24:39,270 --> 00:24:41,100
[Hyeyeon: I love accessories.]

573
00:24:41,100 --> 00:24:42,760
[Hyeyeon: I wear everything except rings.]

574
00:24:42,760 --> 00:24:44,240
[Seungho: Right, you're wearing
a necklace right now.]

575
00:24:43,770 --> 00:24:44,470
Yeah.

576
00:24:44,240 --> 00:24:45,530
[Hyeyeon: And earrings, obviously.]

577
00:24:47,380 --> 00:24:50,180
[Hyeyeon: You don't really wear accessories?]
[Seungho: Usually,]

578
00:24:50,180 --> 00:24:52,630
[Seungho: I'm somewhat into necklaces.]

579
00:24:52,490 --> 00:24:53,840
-You're not wearing one today? -Not...

580
00:24:52,630 --> 00:24:54,610
[Hyeyeon: Not today?]

581
00:24:54,610 --> 00:24:57,670
[Seungho: I was going for a more casual look today.]
[Hyeyeon: It actually... totally works on you today!]

582
00:24:57,670 --> 00:24:59,970
[Hyeyeon: It really suits you.]
[Seungho: Oh, really?]

583
00:24:59,060 --> 00:24:59,570
Yeah.

584
00:24:59,970 --> 00:25:01,490
[Hyeyeon: It looks great on you.]

585
00:25:01,930 --> 00:25:03,440
[Seungho: Your outfit looks great on you too.]

586
00:25:03,440 --> 00:25:05,760
[Hyeyeon: Thanks.]

587
00:25:06,900 --> 00:25:07,920
[Seungho: Once we get back to the house, this...]

588
00:25:07,920 --> 00:25:10,600
[Hyeyeon: They won't notice, right?]

589
00:25:10,600 --> 00:25:12,800
[Seungho: I think they totally will.]
[Hyeyeon: They'll ask what's up with us.]

590
00:25:12,800 --> 00:25:15,950
[Seungho: Exactly.]
[Hyeyeon: What?]

591
00:25:16,190 --> 00:25:17,800
[Hyeyeon: What do you mean?]

592
00:25:21,720 --> 00:25:25,600
[Hyeyeon: We have the same MBTI anyway, ESTP.]

593
00:25:23,370 --> 00:25:23,900
Yes.

594
00:25:24,840 --> 00:25:25,470
Yes.

595
00:25:26,130 --> 00:25:29,570
[Hyeyeon: We say the exact same things.]

596
00:25:29,570 --> 00:25:32,010
[Seungho: Well, ESTPs are...]

597
00:25:32,010 --> 00:25:34,650
[Seungho: usually pretty straightforward.
That's just how we are.]

598
00:25:34,030 --> 00:25:34,610
Yes.

599
00:25:35,390 --> 00:25:37,640
[Hyeyeon: Pretty blunt.]
[Seungho: Exactly.]

600
00:25:37,640 --> 00:25:39,380
[Seungho: We click so well.]
[Hyeyeon: So we keep asking each other questions.]

601
00:25:39,380 --> 00:25:42,020
[Hyeyeon: Like asking each other how we look.]

602
00:25:43,140 --> 00:25:45,870
[Hyeyeon: Just to get an honest answer.]

603
00:25:45,870 --> 00:25:47,590
[Seungho: This morning...]

604
00:25:48,190 --> 00:25:50,570
[They are more in sync than they expected]

605
00:25:50,790 --> 00:25:52,550
[Hyeyeon: Do you like fizzy drinks?]
[Seungho: Yeah.]

606
00:25:52,550 --> 00:25:54,900
[Seungho: I'll drink pretty much any soda.]

607
00:25:54,900 --> 00:25:58,150
[Seungho: Green grape is my favorite.]
[Hyeyeon: Green grape?]

608
00:25:58,150 --> 00:25:59,520
[Hyeyeon: They don't have that here.]

609
00:25:58,220 --> 00:25:59,530
-No green grape here. -Yeah.

610
00:25:59,520 --> 00:26:02,530
[Seungho: True, but I like grapefruit, too.]
[Hyeyeon: You like grapefruit too?]

611
00:26:02,920 --> 00:26:05,490
[Hyeyeon: Ah, so that's why
you're always eating green grapes at the house?]

612
00:26:05,490 --> 00:26:07,300
[Seungho: Uh... I guess... I guess so?]

613
00:26:07,300 --> 00:26:09,520
[Seungho: I've always loved fruit.]

614
00:26:09,520 --> 00:26:10,880
[Hyeyeon: Yeah, me too.]

615
00:26:10,880 --> 00:26:12,660
[Seungho: I love desserts after meals.]

616
00:26:12,810 --> 00:26:15,430
Sweet stuff? The sweeter the better?

617
00:26:13,030 --> 00:26:17,020
[Constantly curious about Seungho]

618
00:26:15,430 --> 00:26:17,020
-Like chocolate. -Chocolate.

619
00:26:17,020 --> 00:26:19,400
[Seungho: I like it,
but instead of super sweet stuff,]

620
00:26:19,400 --> 00:26:21,260
[Seungho: I prefer things that are just right,
so you can keep eating them.]

621
00:26:21,260 --> 00:26:23,250
[Seungho: The kind you can't stop eating.]
[Hyeyeon: Moderately sweet.]

622
00:26:22,280 --> 00:26:23,020
Yeah.

623
00:26:23,250 --> 00:26:25,940
[Hyeyeon: I love raspberries and things like that.]
[Seungho: Ah, raspberries.]

624
00:26:25,940 --> 00:26:28,440
[Hyeyeon: When it comes to dessert,
I choose raspberries over chocolate any day.]

625
00:26:28,440 --> 00:26:30,540
[Hyeyeon: I like lighter desserts.]

626
00:26:30,540 --> 00:26:32,630
[Seungho: Do you usually like
fruit-based desserts?]

627
00:26:32,630 --> 00:26:34,230
[Hyeyeon: Fruit? Yeah, If there's no fruit,
it's not as good.]

628
00:26:34,230 --> 00:26:36,570
[Seungho: So, for cake, you go for strawberry?]
[Hyeyeon: Yes!]

629
00:26:36,570 --> 00:26:38,470
[Hyeyeon: You're not the same?]
[Seungho: Me too.]

630
00:26:42,410 --> 00:26:43,740
-Thank you. -Thank you.

631
00:26:46,200 --> 00:26:47,190
Thanks.

632
00:26:48,220 --> 00:26:49,120
Thank you.

633
00:26:49,340 --> 00:26:51,930
[Seungho: I was going to give it to you,
and you just took it yourself.]

634
00:26:50,430 --> 00:26:50,990
Did I?

635
00:26:54,770 --> 00:26:55,760
[Hyeyeon: You got hurt earlier, right?]

636
00:26:55,760 --> 00:26:57,450
[Seungho: I'm fine.]
[Hyeyeon: Where is it?]

637
00:26:57,450 --> 00:26:59,590
[Seungho: My ankle... and here too.]

638
00:26:58,770 --> 00:26:59,660
And your hand.

639
00:26:59,590 --> 00:27:01,690
[Seungho: This is just a tiny scrape.]

640
00:27:01,690 --> 00:27:04,960
[Seungho: This one's nothing,
but my ankle hurts a bit.]

641
00:27:04,960 --> 00:27:05,920
[Hyeyeon: Did you hurt your ankle, too?]

642
00:27:08,090 --> 00:27:08,870
Oh no.

643
00:27:08,880 --> 00:27:10,930
[Seungho: It's fine, nothing serious.]

644
00:27:09,530 --> 00:27:10,930
Really? Glad to hear that.

645
00:27:10,930 --> 00:27:14,150
[Seungho: I'll just put some ointment on it
when we get back.]

646
00:27:14,150 --> 00:27:15,690
[Hyeyeon: Right, we have some, don't we?]

647
00:27:15,690 --> 00:27:17,590
[Hyeyeon: I'll find it for you
the second we get back.]

648
00:27:17,590 --> 00:27:19,310
[Seungho: Right away?]

649
00:27:19,310 --> 00:27:23,070
[Hyeyeon: After all, I'm the one
who dragged you out here for this—]

650
00:27:23,070 --> 00:27:26,080
[Hyeyeon: intense surfing session out of nowhere.]

651
00:27:26,080 --> 00:27:29,310
[Seungho: I had a blast.]
[Hyeyeon: Really? Awesome.]

652
00:27:29,690 --> 00:27:31,740
[Seungho: I really wanted
to get in the water anyway.]

653
00:27:31,740 --> 00:27:33,180
[Hyeyeon: Oh, same here.]

654
00:27:33,180 --> 00:27:35,220
[Hyeyeon: I brought a swimsuit ]

655
00:27:35,220 --> 00:27:37,870
[Hyeyeon: I kept hoping we'd get to swim.]

656
00:27:37,870 --> 00:27:39,200
[Seungho: Did you have fun?]

657
00:27:39,200 --> 00:27:43,760
[Hyeyeon: Yeah. Honestly, if I went
with someone else, it might have been less fun.]

658
00:27:41,070 --> 00:27:43,270
-It might have been less fun.. -Really?

659
00:27:43,760 --> 00:27:46,470
[Hyeyeon: Feeling flattered?]
[Seungho: Yeah, a little?]

660
00:27:46,470 --> 00:27:47,690
[Shy]

661
00:27:51,780 --> 00:27:54,310
[Hyeyeon: Oh? Did you try it yet?]
[Seungho: Not yet...]

662
00:27:54,570 --> 00:27:55,470
[Seungho: Let's eat together.]

663
00:27:55,470 --> 00:27:56,710
[Hyeyeon: Let's dig in then.]

664
00:27:57,930 --> 00:27:59,590
[Hyeyeon: Let's eat.]

665
00:28:02,450 --> 00:28:03,940
[Hmm!]

666
00:28:05,000 --> 00:28:06,290
[Hmm!]

667
00:28:07,320 --> 00:28:09,720
[Seungho: I feel like we really click
on things like this.]

668
00:28:09,990 --> 00:28:12,450
[Hyeyeon: Just genuine reactions.]

669
00:28:12,820 --> 00:28:16,890
[Seungho: Sometimes we say the exact same words.]
[Hyeyeon: Right.]

670
00:28:17,340 --> 00:28:18,830
[Hyeyeon: Exactly the same.]

671
00:28:20,180 --> 00:28:24,730
[Hyeyeon: I thought you were more reserved at first,
like you hesitated to speak]

672
00:28:24,730 --> 00:28:27,010
[Hyeyeon: back when we first met.]

673
00:28:27,010 --> 00:28:29,520
[Hyeyeon: But strangely...]
[Seungho: Ah, based on looks?]

674
00:28:28,180 --> 00:28:28,820
Yeah.

675
00:28:29,520 --> 00:28:33,690
[Hyeyeon: But you're such an ESTP.]

676
00:28:34,760 --> 00:28:40,520
[Hyeyeon: I totally thought
he was a cautious, quiet guy.]

677
00:28:40,520 --> 00:28:43,750
[Hyeyeon: But he doesn't hold back.
If he has something to say,]

678
00:28:43,750 --> 00:28:45,660
[Hyeyeon: he just comes right out and says it.]

679
00:28:45,980 --> 00:28:48,800
["That caught my attention."]

680
00:28:49,060 --> 00:28:51,680
How did the picture we just took turn out?

681
00:28:51,900 --> 00:28:54,090
[Hyeyeon: Oh? There's a text?]

682
00:28:52,810 --> 00:28:54,210
-Really? Hold on. -Yeah.

683
00:28:54,600 --> 00:28:55,800
Let me check mine too.

684
00:29:02,210 --> 00:29:04,210
[Yongkyu: Hey.]

685
00:29:04,610 --> 00:29:10,480
[Sujin: Hyeyeon, how was surfing?
I want to hear all about it.
You have to tell me later.]

686
00:29:10,480 --> 00:29:14,260
[The texts they both received]

687
00:29:14,440 --> 00:29:17,040
Please read the text.

688
00:29:14,620 --> 00:29:18,340
[The Previous Night]

689
00:29:24,570 --> 00:29:26,580
[Sujin: There's a new mission.]

690
00:29:27,690 --> 00:29:34,400
[The official messaging app "SBM Talk"
has been installed on your phones.
Please use this to communicate.]

691
00:29:35,160 --> 00:29:40,940
[Messages are capped at 7 per day for 7 days, resetting every morning at 7:00 AM.]

692
00:29:42,100 --> 00:29:46,730
[SBM Talk lets you freely
express your feelings on BI-LIVE.]

693
00:29:47,040 --> 00:29:51,420
[Will the cast be more upfront
about their feelings now?]

694
00:29:52,480 --> 00:29:54,300
[Glancing over]

695
00:29:54,300 --> 00:29:57,880
[Seungho: I'm curious.
Keeping it a secret for now?]

696
00:29:58,670 --> 00:30:01,590
[Receiving an SBM Talk during a date]

697
00:30:02,360 --> 00:30:05,300
[Will Hyeyeon let someone else sway her?]

698
00:30:06,670 --> 00:30:08,510
[Hyeyeon: There's something I'm curious about.]

699
00:30:07,710 --> 00:30:08,340
Okay.

700
00:30:09,450 --> 00:30:13,520
[Hyeyeon: Well, just now...
not just now, yesterday.]

701
00:30:13,930 --> 00:30:18,480
[Hyeyeon: You chose Jinwoo in the secret room.]
[Yeah, exactly.]

702
00:30:18,480 --> 00:30:23,360
[Hyeyeon: I didn't think you'd pick him.]

703
00:30:23,360 --> 00:30:27,480
[Hyeyeon: Since you already had a 1-on-1 date.]

704
00:30:29,500 --> 00:30:32,960
[Hyeyeon: I figured you...]

705
00:30:32,960 --> 00:30:39,750
[Hyeyeon: would try to get
to know other people one by one.]

706
00:30:39,750 --> 00:30:43,650
[Hyeyeon: I kept wondering
who you'd pick besides Jinwoo.]

707
00:30:43,650 --> 00:30:47,460
